oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Hortense Parmer
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Hortense Parmer, aunt of Louis Trice II, at the Botanical Gardens in Ft. Worth. Louis was born in Dallas, Texas to Louis E. Trice and Eura Parmer Trice in 1914. His father was born and raised in Montgomery County, Tennessee.
